Node.Description: Go to Accounts payable > Purchase orders > Purchase orders assigned to me.
Click New.
In the Vendor account field, enter or select a value.
In the list, select row 3.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
Click OK.
On the Action Pane, click Purchase order.
In the list, mark the selected row.
In the Item number field, enter or select a value.
In the list, find and select the desired record.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
Click Save.
In the Item number field, enter or select a value.
Close the page.
In the Item number field, enter or select a value.
In the list, select row 7.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
Click Save.
On the Action Pane, click Purchase.
Click Confirm.
Click OK.
On the Action Pane, click Receive.
Click Product receipt.
In the Product receipt field, type a value.
Click OK.
On the Action Pane, click Invoice.
Click Invoice.
In the Number field, type a value.
Click Update match status.
Click Post.
